<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>天機閣 - 專業命理服務</title>
    <meta name="description" content="專業命理服務：今日運勢查詢、紫微斗數、八字命理、姓名學分析、靈籤堂抽籤。">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2d1b3d;
            --secondary: #1a1a2e;
            --accent: #ff6b6b;
            --accent-secondary: #ff8e53;
            --text-light: #ffffff;
            --text-dark: #333333;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Microsoft JhengHei', sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
            color: var(--text-light);
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b6b, #ff8e53);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #ffd166;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
        }
        
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            color: #4ecdc4;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: 1px solid #4ecdc4;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .back-link:hover {
            background: #4ecdc4;
            color: white;
        }
        
        /* 今日運勢區塊 - 置頂 */
        .fortune-section {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,213,102,0.2);
        }
        
        .fortune-section h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ffd166;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .fortune-form {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #ffd166;
        }
        
        .form-group input,
        .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,107,0.3);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group select:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }
        
        .submit-button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b6b, #ff8e53);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .submit-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255,107,107,0.3);
        }
        
        /* 運勢結果中間廣告 */
        .result-ad {
            background: rgba(255,107,107,0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,107,0.3);
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .result-ad h4 {
            color: #ffd166;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .result-ad p {
            color: #aaa;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .result-ad-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 120px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .result-ad-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #ff6b6b;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .result-ad-button:hover {
            background: #ff8e53;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        /* 服務項目 */
        .services {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }
        
        .service-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255,107,107,0.2);
        }
        
        .service-icon {
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--accent);
        }
        
        .service-card h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #ffd166;
        }
        
        .service-card p {
            color: #aaa;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .service-features {
            list-style: none;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .service-features li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #ccc;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        
        .service-features li::before {
            content: '✦';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--accent);
        }
        
        .service-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .service-button:hover {
            background: #ff8e53;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255,107,107,0.3);
        }
        
        /* 靈籤堂按鈕樣式 */
        .fortune-stick-btn {
            background: rgba(157, 78, 221, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(157, 78, 221, 0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .fortune-stick-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(157, 78, 221, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            border-color: #9d4edd;
        }
        
        /* 廣告區域 - 所有廣告都有圖案 */
        .ad-section {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,107,0.2);
        }
        
        .ad-section h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--accent);
        }
        
        .ad-section p {
            color: #ffd166;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .ad-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }
        
        .ad-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,107,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .ad-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255,107,107,0.2);
        }
        
        .ad-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        
        .ad-card h4 {
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .ad-card p {
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            min-height: 40px;
        }
        
        .ad-meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .ad-category {
            color: var(--accent);
            background: rgba(255,107,107,0.1);
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .ad-price {
            color: #ffd166;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .ad-button {
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b6b, #ff8e53);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .ad-button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff8e53, #ff6b6b);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255,107,107,0.3);
        }
        
        /* 跳出廣告樣式 */
        .popup-ad {
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.9);
            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.95);
            border: 2px solid #ff6b6b;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 400px;
            z-index: 1000;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        
        .popup-ad.active {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1);
        }
        
        .popup-ad h3 {
            color: #ffd166;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .popup-ad p {
            color: #aaa;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .popup-ad .ad-content {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .popup-ad .popup-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 120px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .popup-ad .close-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: 15px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 24px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .popup-ad .close-btn:hover {
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }
        
        .popup-ad .popup-button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b6b, #ff8e53);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .popup-ad .popup-button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff8e53, #ff6b6b);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            z-index: 999;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .overlay.active {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
        }
        
        /* 小方塊廣告 */
        .mini-ad {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.9);
            border: 1px solid #4ecdc4;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            width: 250px;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            transform: translateY(100px);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }
        
        .mini-ad.show {
            transform: translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
        }
        
        .mini-ad h4 {
            color: #4ecdc4;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .mini-ad p {
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .mini-ad .mini-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 80px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .mini-ad .mini-button {
            display: block;
            background: #4ecdc4;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .mini-ad .close-mini {
            position: absolute;
            top: 5px;
            right: 5px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            margin-top: 60px;
            color: #aaa;
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .footer-links a {
            color: #aaa;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: #ffd166;
        }
        
        .copyright {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }
            
            .subtitle {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            
            .services {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .ad-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .footer-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .popup-ad {
                width: 95%;
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .mini-ad {
                width: 200px;
                right: 10px;
                bottom: 10px;
            }
            
            .result-ad-image {
                height: 100px;
            }
            
            .fortune-stick-btn {
                padding: 12px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 跳出廣告 -->
    <div class="overlay" id="overlay"></div>
    
    <div class="popup-ad" id="popupAd">
        <button class="close-btn" onclick="closePopupAd()">×</button>
        <h3>推薦商品</h3>
        <div class="ad-content">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544716278-ca5e3f4abd8c?w=400&h=200&fit=crop" alt="推薦商品" class="popup-image">
            <h4 id="popupAdTitle">精選生活用品</h4>
            <p id="popupAdDesc">精選生活用品，提升生活品質</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 14px; color: #ffd166;">
                <span id="popupAdCategory">書籍雜誌</span> • 
                
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="popup-button" onclick="visitAd()">查看詳情</button>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 靈籤堂彈出視窗 -->
    <div class="popup-ad" id="fortuneStickPopup" style="max-width: 500px; border-color: #9d4edd;">
        <button class="close-btn" onclick="closeFortuneStick()">×</button>
        <h3>🎋 靈籤堂 - 線上抽籤</h3>
        <div class="ad-content">
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <div style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 15px;">🎋</div>
                <h4>選擇您想詢問的主題</h4>
            </div>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <button class="fortune-stick-btn" onclick="drawFortuneStick('general')">
                    <div style="font-size: 24px;">🔮</div>
                    <div>綜合運勢</div>
                </button>
                <button class="fortune-stick-btn" onclick="drawFortuneStick('love')">
                    <div style="font-size: 24px;">❤️</div>
                    <div>感情婚姻</div>
                </button>
                <button class="fortune-stick-btn" onclick="drawFortuneStick('career')">
                    <div style="font-size: 24px;">💼</div>
                    <div>事業工作</div>
                </button>
                <button class="fortune-stick-btn" onclick="drawFortuneStick('wealth')">
                    <div style="font-size: 24px;">💰</div>
                    <div>財運投資</div>
                </button>
                <button class="fortune-stick-btn" onclick="drawFortuneStick('health')">
                    <div style="font-size: 24px;">🏥</div>
                    <div>健康狀況</div>
                </button>
                <button class="fortune-stick-btn" onclick="drawFortuneStick('study')">
                    <div style="font-size: 24px;">📚</div>
                    <div>學業考試</div>
                </button>
                <button class="fortune-stick-btn" onclick="drawFortuneStick('family')">
                    <div style="font-size: 24px;">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</div>
                    <div>家庭關係</div>
                </button>
                <button class="fortune-stick-btn" onclick="drawFortuneStick('travel')">
                    <div style="font-size: 24px;">✈️</div>
                    <div>旅行外出</div>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div id="fortuneStickResult" style="display: none;">
                <div style="background: rgba(157, 78, 221, 0.1); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid rgba(157, 78, 221, 0.3);">
                    <h4 id="stickTitle" style="color: #9d4edd; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 15px;"></h4>
                    <div id="stickContent" style="color: #aaa; line-height: 1.6;"></div>
                    <div style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;">
                        <button class="popup-button" onclick="drawFortuneStickAgain()" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #9d4edd, #6a0dad);">再抽一次</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 小方塊廣告 -->
    <div class="mini-ad" id="miniAd">
        <button class="close-mini" onclick="closeMiniAd()">×</button>
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513475382585-d06e58bcb0e0?w=200&h=100&fit=crop" alt="精選內衣" class="mini-image">
        <h4>今日精選推薦</h4>
        <p>根據您的運勢結果，為您推薦精選生活用品</p>
        <a href="https://www.ichannels.com.tw/product/example?member=3QWtn<a href="#" class="mini-button" onclick="trackMiniAd()">立即查看</a>track=mini-ad" class="mini-button" onclick="trackMiniAd(); return false;">立即查看</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>🔮 天機閣 - 專業命理服務</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">已上線服務：今日運勢查詢、紫微斗數、八字命理、姓名學分析、手相面相解讀、靈籤堂抽籤</p>
            <a href="../" class="back-link">← 返回入口網站</a>
        </header>
        
        <!-- 今日運勢 - 置頂 -->
        <section class="fortune-section">
            <h2>今日運勢查詢</h2>
            <div class="fortune-form">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="birth-date">出生年月日</label>
                    <input type="date" id="birth-date" name="birth-date" required>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="question-type">想詢問的事項</label>
                    <select id="question-type" name="question-type">
                        <option value="general">綜合運勢</option>
                        <option value="career">事業工作</option>
                        <option value="love">感情婚姻</option>
                        <option value="wealth">財運投資</option>
                        <option value="health">健康狀況</option>
                        <option value="study">學業考試</option>
                        <option value="family">家庭關係</option>
                        <option value="travel">旅行外出</option>
                        <option value="decision">重要決策</option>
                        <option value="opportunity">機會運勢</option>
                        <option value="relationship">人際關係</option>
                        <option value="creativity">創意靈感</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit" class="submit-button" onclick="getFortune()">
                    🔮 獲取今日運勢
                </button>
                
                <div id="fortune-result" style="margin-top: 30px; display: none;">
                    <div style="background: rgba(255,213,102,0.1); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,213,102,0.3);">
                        <h3 style="color: #ffd166; margin-bottom: 15px;">您的今日運勢</h3>
                        <div id="fortune-content"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- 服務項目 -->
        <section class="services">
            <div class="service-card" onclick="showServiceAd('紫微斗數命盤', '舒適內衣推薦')">
                <div class="service-icon">♈️</div>
                <h3>紫微斗數命盤</h3>
                <p>專業紫微斗數排盤，分析命盤格局、大運流年，深入解讀人生軌跡與發展方向。</p>
                <ul class="service-features">
                    <li>完整命盤製作</li>
                    <li>十二宮位分析</li>
                    <li>大運流年推算</li>
                    <li>專業命理師解讀</li>
